OL,3,CUK creates Nobel prize winners, but
OL,4,Cdoes not reap benefits
OL,6,FIt is testament to the UK's world-
OL,7,Fclass education system that four of
OL,8,Fthis year's Nobel prize winners (so
OL,9,Ffar) were born and educated in the UK.
OL,11,FThey are Johnson and Robinson for
OL,12,Feconomics (announced today), Hinton
OL,13,Ffor physics and Hassabis for chemistry.
