OL,3,CUK creates Nobel prize winners, but
OL,4,Cdoes not reap benefits
OL,6,FThis is cause for pride and
OL,7,Fcelebration. But it is also profoundly
OL,8,Fdepressing that to fulfil their
OL,9,Fextraordinary potential, all four felt
OL,10,Fobliged either to move to North
OL,11,FAmerican universities (Johnson,
OL,12,FRobinson and Hinton) or take US
OL,13,Fmegabucks (from Google - Hassabis, and
OL,14,Fto a lesser extent Hinton).
