OL,3,CUK creates Nobel prize winners, but
OL,4,Cdoes not reap benefits
OL,6,FIn other words, their success shows
OL,7,Fboth the success and the weakness of
OL,8,Fthe UK.
OL,10,FWe create the so-called human capital,
OL,11,Fbut the fruits of these outstanding
OL,12,Fbrains are routinely reaped by other
OL,13,Fcountries and economies, usually the
OL,14,FUS.
OL,16,FAny British government should surely
OL,17,Ffocus on what needs to change to
OL,18,Fretain great British talent, and the
OL,19,Fcommercial revenues their ideas spawn,
OL,20,Fat home.
